NAME		followup
SYNTAX		followup [-e] <note number>
DESCRIPTION	Followup a board note. The subject of your new note is
		set to 'Re: ' plus the subject of the note you are following
		up and the note body is copied and quoted.

		If the -e argument is supplied, your reply will be sent to
		the original poster via email, rather than being posted to
		the board.

		Excessive quoting is discouraged, quote relevant parts only.
SEE ALSO	post, epost, quotechar
